    - Working/Script Directories
    - Git Repo Info

0.1.1 2014-03-11

  - Add tests
  - Fix issue when CLI option is multiple words surrounded by quotes

0.1.0 2014-03-07

  - Easily archive and reproduce Perl-based analyses

